¡Buenas noches! ✨

Hoy os traigo un post con mis productos más utilizados en estos días 🥰 con nuevos favoritos y algún producto que me ha dejado un poco meh 🥺 (no siempre me puede gustar todo 🤭)

Los productos en cuestión son los siguientes: 

✨Base Eaze Drop✨ fentybeauty : ya sabéis que me encanta esta base porque aporta una cobertura ligera modulable y un efecto “blur” muy bonito 🥰 Queda la piel preciosa con ella (eso si, yo solo puedo utilizarla cuando tengo la piel muy bien porque sino me remarca hasta el alma 💀) 

✨Corrector True Skin✨ catrice.cosmetics : es un viejo conocido por aquí 😅 Ya sabéis que me encanta su cobertura y lo bonita que deja la zona de la ojera, no cuartea nada. También me va genial para tapar imperfecciones 🫶🏻

✨Máscara Pure Volume✨ catrice.cosmetics : Esta máscara de pestañas me la regaló eme.skincare cuando fui a visitarla porque no le gustaba y yo tengo que decir que tampoco me apasiona 🫠 No noto ninguna diferencia respecto a otras que he tenido, me gustan infinitamente mas la Lift up de Catrice y la Double Trouble de Essence 💘 No es una mala mascara de pestañas pero supongo que esperaba más 🥺

✨Colorete Soft Pinch✨ rarebeauty : lo habeis visto por aqui trillones de veces, me encanta esta formula 😍 NECESITO los tonos Hope y Encourage, por favor sephora reponedlos de una vez 😭😭😭😭😭

✨Labial mate 101✨ deliplus_beauty : es un nude suuuuper bonito y muy favorecedor. Estoy enamorada y el cambio de packaging con la tapa imantada me parece todo un acierto 💖 

Contadme, ¿habéis probado alguno? ¿Cuáles os llaman la atención? ¡Os leo! 🙈

fentyskin Do you remember?  fenty I bought my first FENTY SKIN START'R SET a few days ago and it was really good!!! I liked (✔️Total Cleans'r) because it was so refreshing after washing, and it smelled really nice. (✔️Fat Water) was very comfortable to use, it refreshed my skin, and I was glad that it didn't feel sticky afterwards.  I use (✔️Hydra Vizor) as a moisturizing cream in the morning, and since it has SPF 30, using it before makeup saves time on busy mornings, and it's convenient because I can apply sunscreen and moisturizer in only one step.  This is because it is troublesome to apply all moisturizing cream, sunscreen, and primer.  It's really amazing all.  These were the small size, so these products I would definitely repeat and buy the big ones!  Great, fentyskin 🤍🤍

FENTY SKIN START'R SET

-Total Cleans'r

✔ Barbados Cherry (Acerola): Loaded with more Vitamin C than an orange; helps brighten skin 

✔ Ginkgo Biloba: Helps control surface oil and clarify skin; a popular traditional Chinese ingredient

-Fat Water

✔ Australian Lemon Myrtle: Helps reduce surface oil and refine pores 

✔ Japanese Raisin Tree: Helps detoxify—commonly used in Asia to recover from long nights of partying

-Hydra Vizor

✔ Kalahari Melon: Delivers vitamin and antioxidant-packed hydration 

✔ Niacinamide: Fights shine and reduces the look of pores and dark spots

Aging skin.. most of us are experiencing it (unfortunately). This AM routine focuses on fortifying the skin barrier bc we all know that that’s the key to bouncy, glowing, youthful skin 💦

✨ paulaschoice Ultra-Gentle Cleanser* - Non-foaming cleanser that’s true to its name. Doesn’t leave the skin feeling squeaky clean, but it gets the job done.

✨ laneige_us Cream Skin Toner and Moisturizer - Milky goodness in a bottle. Wouldn’t say it replaces your moisturizer but it is super hydrating. Love how the texture is watery so I can pack on 2 layers without it feeling suffocating.

✨ paulaschoice Pro-Collagen Multi-Peptide Booster* - New in my skincare arsenal. It makes my skin so plump. Doesn’t pill and absorbs into the pores immediately too. Only qualm I have is that it has a vinegar scent, but luckily, it doesn’t linger.

✨ glowrecipe Guava Vitamin C Eye Cream* - Holy grail status AND a forever repurchase. It brightens, hydrates without feeling greasy, and preps the eye for makeup. Containing peptides, green caffeine, vitamin c, it is a true multitasker that literally targets all of your under-eye concerns.

✨ rovectin_us Lotus Cream* - Need a backup of this asap. The gel texture applies like silk on my skin. It’s not tacky and keeps my face moisturized all day. Definitely suitable for all skin types and all year round.

✨ skin1004official Hyalu-Cica Water Fit Sun Serum* - This chemical spf blends in like a dream. No white cast, eye sting, or pilling. I could skip out on moisturizer if I wanted to bc it’s THAT moisturizing. Would repurchase!

(*) = gifted

Product: Rare Beauty Liquid Touch Weightless Foundation
Price: $30
Review: I can safely say I have almost tried all the foundations popular brands have to offer primarily because I am always up for trying and reviewing new make up products and finding the best in each category. 

Okay so here is my take on this one! The formula is very liquidy, start with a drop and then build it up gradually depending on how much coverage you would prefer. The approach is ‘less is more’. This foundation works best for those who have balanced skin. A few extra steps will be needed for those with oily or dry skin. Oily skin users will need a primer that controls oil and a face/setting powder is a must post application while the dry skin users need to moisturize really really well. 

The result after using this foundation was an air brushed and natural looking skin. However, If you have pores or dark spots you may need to build up the coverage or opt for a concealer. Another interesting thing is that the foundation has an applicator instead of a pump which may or may not matter to you but for me pump works better. This foundation may not be the best of the ones I have tried but it can be a good everyday use option. It doesn’t beat the finish I get from Dior Foreever Skin Glow or Armani Luminous Silk Perfect Glow who are in the same light buildable category. 
So i will rate this foundation a 7/10
I definitely liked Rare Beauty Liquid Blush much better.

Viele von euch wissen ja das ich täglich ein Wimpernserum benutze.
Ich bin jetzt mal auf das GrandeLash-MD Lash Enhanching Serum von grandecosmetics umgestiegen, aber die 0,1ml Version. Die ist ganz praktisch zum Testen für einen Monat (gerade auch was die Verträglichkeit angeht). 

Nach einem Monat kann man hier schon längere und dichtere Wimpern erkennen 🥰 Die "volle Wirkung" natürlich erst nach knapp 3 Monaten. Heißt aber auch ☝🏼 täglich anwenden damit das ganze auch was bringt. 

Hauptvorteile:
– Wirkt schon beim ersten Auftrag
– Trägt zu natürlich längeren und dichteren Wimpern bei
– Kompatibel mit Kontaktlinsen und Wimpernverlängerungen
– Augenärztlich getestet
– Nicht an Tieren getestet
– Ohne Parabene 

Einmal täglich wie ein Eyeliner direkt am Wimpernkranz auftragen, nicht auf die Wimpern selbst 😉 (ich benutze es immer vor dem Schlafengehen) 

Habt ihr schonmal ein Wimpernserum benutzt oder habt ihr von Natur aus schöne Wimpern? ☺️

✅ RECENSIONE DEL ROSSETTO YSL✅ trovato nel calendario dell' avvento yslbeauty comprato da sephoraitalia
"Il rossetto è uno di quei prodotti a cui pochissimi sanno rinunciare."
Oggi vi parlo di uno dei rossetti di YSL, che nonostante  hanno il finish cremoso e la texture idratante non sbavano ed hanno una buona durata. L'iconico rossetto firmato YSL idratante protettivo ed iperpigmentato, che dona alle tue labbra un confortevole effetto seta e le rende più abbaglianti. Fin dalla sua creazione nel 1978, Rouge Pur Couture è stato il manifesto di una donna audace e indipendente, che rompe le regole per reinventarsi. Rouge pur couture veste le labbra con una gamma di colori iperpigmentati. L’involucro dorato è stato ripensato in un gioco di tensione estetica tra opulenza e minimalismo.
Rouge Pur Couture comprende una gamma di tonalità uniche ed ispirate ai colori caratteristici di YSL: il Rosso, il Fucsia, l'Arancione e il Nudo.
🔴IL ROSSO: L’audace tonalità della passione, un pilastro di assoluta femminilità, una spinta ad agire.IL FUCSIA: Un colore audace, congelato in pieno fioritura. La quintessenza di una condotta scandalosa, riportata in vita dall’emozione della passerella parigina.
🟠L’ARANCIONE: L’iniezione di vigore, di passione e delizia. Un simbolo di incanto, speranza, spontaneità.
⚪IL NUDO: Autentico, puro, un colore couture che veste le labbra, intrise di sensualità, raggianti di charm.
È un rossetto di lunga durata, Idratante, Antiossidante
 ❤️quello che vedete qui nel post
 - Le Rouge
la tonalità è pigmentata e piena, il finish è morbido e cremoso, la stesura molto piacevole. ( Sfogliate lo vedete anche sulle mie labbra)
Questi rossetti non tendono minimamente a sbavare, mi è davvero piaciuto, ha disponibile una gamma di colorazioni molto ampia e la performance ottima. Non è facile trovare dei rossetti così  idratanti e  anche duraturi. 
E voi? L avete mai provato?
Lo trovate nelle migliori profumerie ( Sephora, ecc.)

The new Mehndi Moment Blush ($28) by the brand Kulfi.beauty just launched at the end of January sephora and I was one of the first to try it out! #gifted

There are 5 beautiful shades to choose from. The shade here is "Sandalwood Swirls' a neutral mauve color.

Key Ingredients:

🌷 Amla Extract- Rich in protective antioxidants to fight against free radicals

🌷 Hibiscus Extract- Boosts moisture and hydrates the skin

I have to say I am a big fan of cream products and this one knocked it out of the park. I fell in love with this blush the first time I applied it and the moment I felt its texture. In my opinion it is beginner proof for anyone who is just getting into cream products because it's very easy to blend but also it looks and feels so luxurious and makes the cheeks look perfectly flushed and healthy. It's a very lightweight, moussey texture and a little goes a long way in terms of pigment and application. The color might look intense but it doesn't have to be. I can go light-handed and it applies so effortlessly without separating the foundation underneath. There's no stickiness or too much shine just a beautiful application of color that lasts pretty much the whole day. I really like the shades and the one I have is perfect for me! I love the brand already and can't wait to try more from them.

Have you heard of this brand? The brand name, Kulfi, is a colorful and delicious South Asian ice cream 😋🍨 what a delightful name! It is a brand that donates to mental health organizations which I think is amazing! Check them out! Link is on my stories 🥰

O que é: um mini rolo facial de duas peças para áreas específicas do rosto e olhos com uma bolsa de veludo fofa para armazenamento. 

Dois rolos para dois efeitos: o rolo liso de alumínio permanece frio e ajuda com a aparência de inchaço, já o rolo de silicone é bom para massagear a pele. Cada efeito melhora a circulação natural para uma pele brilhante e de aparência saudável, além de ajudar a liberar a tensão dos músculos faciais. O rolo pode ser usado sozinho ou com óleos ou creme para melhor absorção.

Uso sugerido:
 -Use o mini rolo após limpar, tonificar e hidratar.
 -Rolar pela testa e ao redor dos olhos, contornos do rosto e pescoço.
 -Lave-o após o uso.

Paletkę cieni Babydoll r.e.m.beauty kupiłam w sephorapolska zupełnie przypadkowo. Szukałam poręcznej paletki w odcieniach nude (a jakżeby inaczej 😄), którą mogłabym zabierać ze sobą na wyjazdy. 
Opakowanie paletki przypomina mi trochę dawne opakowania kosmetyków z Avonu🙈🙈🙈 Szczerze mówiąc marka sygnowana nazwiskiem Ariany Grande mogłaby pomyśleć o lepszym wyglądzie produktów. Na szczęście zawartość okazała się lepsza niż opakowanie. 

Paletka zawiera 6 neutralnych  odcieni,zarówno matowych jak i błyszczących. Cienie płynnie się blendują i wszystkie są dobrze napigmentowane. Nie miałam problemu z rozprowadzeniem ich na powiece (ale uwaga,ja wszystkie cienie kładę na Glitter Primer z nyxcosmetics). Zdecydowanie jest to paletka idealna do podróży oraz dla osób,które zaczynają swoją przygodę z makijażem (na pewno nie zrobią sobie tą paletka żadnych nieestetycznych placków). 
Najbardziej podoba mi się formuła błysków,ponieważ są bardzo kremowe. 

Markę R.E.M. Beauty znajdziecie w sephorapolska
Szczerze przyznam,że z produktów 
R.E.M. Beauty tylko ta paletka cieni mi się spodobała. Reszta, w mojej opinii, to takie meh....

The planet of love, beauty, cooperation, and material pleasures, Venus is often a makeup artists favorite planet 🥰 

Venus in astrology embodies all things of love and beauty. Venus symbolizes our love language and how we give and receive love. It symbolizes all of our partnerships, including relationships, business, and every area of life where we cooperate with another. Venus shows our love (or disdain) of material pleasures, and can show (along with midheaven/10th house) how we can best earn our money. Those with a strong sense of aesthetics and beauty typically have an exalted, domicile, or well aspected Venus placement in their chart. However, a Venus that is challenged or otherwise afflicted can symbolize troubles with love and finances. 

Where is your Venus? Mine is obviously in Capricorn 🥴💕

✔️pełnego krycia
✔️lekkiej formuły -nie chcę mieć tony makijażu na twarzy,a zależy mi na przykryciu zaczerwienień. Myślę,że każdej z nas zależy na świeżym i ładnym wyglądzie,ale mając niewielką ilość podkładu na twarzy. 

Tak,tak,wiem,że trudno znaleźć takie połączenie w przypadku kryjących podkładów,ale mnie się udaje trafić na perełki,które potem tu polecam 🤗🤎 

Zależy mi też na tym,aby podklad wytrzymał na twarzy cały dzień,a mój każdy dzień jest intensywny. Tarte Face Tap jest bardzo trwały-mnie trzyma się bez zarzutu ponad 12 godzin. Nie zbiera się w zmarszczkach czy załamaniach cery . Nie wysusza ani nie powoduje dyskomfortu w postaci ściągnięcia skóry. 

Do wyboru mamy mnóstwo odcien tego podkładu i, na pewno dobierzecie idealny dla siebie 🤎🤎🤎

NARS is a brand everybody loves to love. With a range of industry icons, they’re known for their exquisite formulas that are perfect for any occasion. With an option for everybody, you’ll find NARS in every beauty fanatic’s makeup collection. Let me talk you through a few of my favourite products…

🖤 SOFT MATTE COMPLETE CONCEALER

The ultimate spot covering concealer and my secret weapon product to have a great skin day everyday. The smallest amount covers spots in an instance, no matter how inflamed they are. With a soft matte finish, it lasts all day on the skin. I wish I’d had it in my collection sooner. 

🖤 SMUDGE PROOF EYESHADOW BASE

Another one of my secret weapon products: The Smudge Proof Eyeshadow Base ensures my eyeshadow never ever creases, no matter how many hours have gone by since application. It may seem like a product you don’t need, but I never do my makeup without it as it works so well. 

🖤 HIGHLIGHTING POWDER

I love my skin to be radiant and glowy, but I don’t want anything too intense. The NARS Highlighting Powder has a fine formula that allows the skin to look dewy without having an overly metallic finish. It’s brilliant for everyday makeup or those no-makeup makeup moments. 

To explore my thoughts on all the NARS products I’ve tried, you can read my brand review now on victoriavale.com 🖤

This dry shampoo is perfect for those on-the-go days, post-workout refreshes, and extending the life of your blowout.

Aquelas em que a cabeça não pára com mil e umas coisas e não nos deixa dormir? Ou simplesmente os nossos filhos nos tiram umas horas de sono? 😅
Bem depois dessas noites este é o meu segredo... sabem quando ficamos com os olhos inchados, pesados, com olheiras fundas e escuras? 
Pois bem se sofres do mesmo este produto é para ti. 

Aplico estes patches FortifEYE da pixibeauty e dá logo uma sensação tão boa, tão refrescante...

e 10 minutos é o suficiente!!

Bem não sei se é certo fazer isso, nas lojas e sites não tem nenhuma indicação para o fazer, mas como é um produto para aplicar na área dos olhos eu guardo no frigorífico... sim se a sensação é boa quando aplicamos os adesivos, imagina geladinhos... 

Eu mal comprei coloquei logo no frigorífico, guardo outros adesivos e máscaras do tipo também, se é para a área dos olhos ainda vai ajudar mais quando se trata de olhos cansados e inchados... certo ou não eu faço e resulta comigo. 

Se pretenderes experimentar este produto, tem atenção na hora de  escolher o mais indicado para ti, no momento existem 3, o meu é o FortifEYE com colagénio botânico, cafeína e peptídeos que ajudam para um efeito de firmeza, levantamento, suavidade... regeneram, revitalizam, rejuvenescem, reparam e hidratam em profundidade. 

Experimentem colocar no frigorífico e a sensação vai ser 3x melhor e imediata, caso tenhas outros adesivos para colocar na área dos olhos coloca no frigorífico... experimenta e vê a diferença! 

Fica a dica! 

Tens algum produto favorito para a área dos olhos?
Já experimentas te estes patches?

Еще один провал в новых тональных - тональная сыворотка #RoseInc Luminous Tinted Serum 🙄

С одной стороны она прекрасна: легчайшая текстура, в составе ни капли масла, спирта и отдушек, при этом отличный набор увлажняюще-антиоксидантных компонентов, включая сквалан, гиалуроновую, экстракты тамаринда и мангостина, пептиды и витамин Е

Текстура очень похожа на подобные тонирующие продукты #chanel и #erborian - в прозрачном геле плавают инкапсулированные пигменты, перед нанесением их надо смешать кистью или пальцами - получается однородная текстура как у обычного тонального, только легкая и водянистая

Что же тебе Галочка снова не так? Все же отлично 🤨😝

Этот чудо-гель совсем не дает блюр, не выравнивает визуально поры, и в целом ложится не слишком ровно, к тому же некрасиво очерчивает все мельчайшие неровности, превращая их в видимые и некрасивые, при том что у меня в целом ровная кожа, на которой особо выравнивать нечего, я редко пользуюсь тональными! Посмотрите на фото 7 - там я растушевала его на руке, и видно, как он подчеркнул все тонкие линии, кожа выглядит сухой, хотя это не так… Для меня это тональный, который делает кожу визуально хуже, а не лучше. И достаточно быстро во многих местах он просто исчезает, выглядит все это совсем некрасиво 🥺

Тон:
040 - светлый нейтральный беж, оказался для моей светлой кожи даже чуть более осветляющим, чем надо было, я с ним выгляжу бледной (проблем со светлыми оттенками точно нет)

Вот кремовые румяна этой марки - восторг, а эту чудо-сыворотку в топку, не мой вариант. Хотя, кстати, я добавляю ее в плотные тональные, и так она хорошо идет, но сама по себе - нет-нет-нет 🙅‍♀️

Happy Wednesday! Today is the middle of the week and I’m glad to say the hardest part of the week is done! I am absolutely exhausted from these past two days and I am amazed I found the strength to do a super long skincare routine after showering today. It was my exfoliating night so I used the glowrecipe mask for a physical and chemical exfoliation and then followed that by toner, essence and then the Petitfée eye masks and pibuwang sheet mask. My skin was feeling super dry so I was blasting my face with all the hydrating products I had lol. My lips were also feeling super dry and chapped so I decided to treat them to a nice scrub, mask and sleeping mask to help lock in extra moisture. 

Days like this make me feel thankful I have something to look forward to at the end of the day. Something small like a skincare routine can really be the self-care boost I need even when I’m super exhausted. Here’s to self-care and taking care of our mental health even when life can get chaotic.

How do the charlottetilbury & rarebeauty highlighter formulas compare? From wearing these formulas so often and interchangeably, here is what I’ve gathered: 

Texture: in my own words, the CT formula has more of that soft powdery feel to the touch whereas RB has a smooth silky touch. CT describes her formula as a “satin” texture whereas RB describes her formula as a “glass-like sheen” and that is 100% accurate and the best way to describe each individually.

Color: in my swatch photos, we have Champagne Glow from CT (top) & Exhilarate from RB (bottom). You can clearly see that the tone of Exhilarate is far more golden than Champagne Glow which has a true champagne undertone. However, I find on the face I cannot tell a difference.

The number one most asked question I have gotten recently is “which one is your favorite and the one you recommend?” I honestly cannot choose because I love them both so much 😆 but in all seriousness, do you NEED both? No. I would say it depends on what you like in a glow and how much you are wanting to spend. If you like more of a lit from within glow than go with the CT because of that satin texture but if you prefer something more intense than RB is the way to go. 

The CT retails for $48 USD ($6.85/gram)
The RB retails for $25 USD ($8.92/gram)

Além de todas essas dicas, fique sempre de olho ao caminhar pela cidade, pois você pode encontrar verdadeiras joias escondidas em charmosas vielas, com roupas, bolsas, sapatos e artigos incríveis.

Na Via dei Giubbonari pertinho do Campo de' Fiori e na Via dei Coronari ao lado da Piazza Navona você também encontrará preciosas lojas com artigos de excelente qualidade. 

O bairro de Monti também abriga excelentes opções de compras, concentrando várias lojas de Second Hand, artigos vintage e produções artesanais.

Faltou só mencionar uma coisa: Fazer compras caminhando pelas ruas mais charmosas da Itália é um privilégio que só Roma proporciona!

Hello tout le monde, j’espère que vous allez bien ? 💬

Aujourd’hui, je vais vous présenter le mascara « Better Than Sex » de chez toofaced en collaboration avec sananas2106 ! 

Tout d’abord,commençons par le packaging. Il est féminin, très ressemblant au goût de Sananas avec son rose gold et l’effet de la peau à crocodile. La brosse est en poils, un peu disposés dans tous les sens et elle est assez grosse et fournie. C’est exactement le genre de brosse que j’aime utiliser, je trouve que c’est hyper pratique pour attraper tous les cils, même les plus petits et que ça dépose vraiment pas mal de matière. 

L’application est très simple, en un seul passage mes cils sont intensifiés grâce à la pigmentation du mascara. Mes cils sont vraiment allongés et légèrement recourbés. L’effet volume est également présent et la matière est déposée de façon bien uniforme dès la racine des cils, ce qui est top !
Le mascara tient bien tout au long de la journée et/ou soirée.

J’avais lu et entendu qu’il s’effritait avec le temps et pouvait laisser des petits résidus sur les joues et qu’il séchait très vite au fil du temps. Il est au prix de 22€ chez sephorafrance ! C’est un prix plutôt élevé comparé aux mascaras de supermarché mais ce n’est pas non plus le prix d’une marque de luxe, donc je trouve le prix correct.

sephorauk Ling awaited store March open date revealed. Sephora’s first bricks-and-mortar store in the UK will open at Westfield White City in West London on 8 March 2023. The new 6,000sqft retail space includes a dedicated beauty hub which offers beauty services and treatments. Other additions include Sephora’s first Lip Bar and a Hot on Social corner, consisting of a curation of top trending products on social media. The store is located on the same stretch of the shopping centre housing beauty retailers Lush, L’Occitane, Space NK, Boots and Rituals. “This new store will showcase best-in-class beauty expertise and provide unique services to UK customers, including make-up, skin care, hair care, fragrance, body and personalised gifting,” said Sarah Boyd, UK Country Manager. “We cannot wait to welcome our first customers.” Makeup by Mario, GXVE by Gwen Stefani, ONE/SIZE by Patrick Starrr, Vegamour, Skinfix and Commodity will feature exclusively at the UK store. Other brands such as Fenty Beauty, Drunk Elephant, ILIA, R.E.M. Beauty and Jo Malone will also be available. Sephora continues to be a powerhouse retailer in the beauty arena, and was recently credited for being the driving force behind LVMH’s record-breaking year in 2022. Sephora’s performance was highlighted for the company's Selective Retailing category, which saw revenues increase by 26% during the year. This contributed to a 23% increase in revenues to €79.2bn and profits of €21.1bn for the luxury conglomerate in 2022

Fraîche et tendre, Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet est une eau de toilette facettée et spontanée. Cette composition est l'image olfactive d'un généreux bouquet de fleurs tout juste écloses, dont l'intensité fait écho à la tendresse.

Le sillage de l'eau de toilette Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet s'ouvre sur des notes de rose Damanesca et de pivoine, sublimées par la bergamote de Calabre et enveloppées par un voile de muscs blancs. La fraîcheur et la vivacité de l'eau de toilette sont ainsi contrebalancées par une note réconfortante.

Le flacon de Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet est désormais habillé du nœud couture de la fragrance iconique Miss Dior : un ruban jacquard multicolore, aussi raffiné que délicat.

💄Rouge G Rouge A Lèvres édition Limitée Red Orchid 

Guerlain révèle la collection Red Orchid inspiré par les couleurs vibrantes de l'orchidée.

On y retrouve un trio de teintes rouge G inspirés de trois variétés d’orchidées Rouge : 
Mat Velours - N°770 Red Vanda 
Satin - N°918 Red Ballerina 
Mat Métallique - N°966 Red Firestar 

💄J'ai reçu la teinte 966 Red Firestar, je vous laisse découvrir le très bel écrin et la couleur de ce rouge à lèvres à travers mes photos et ma vidéo, c'est un rouge brique métallisé.

💄 Un rouge à lèvres avec une formule exceptionnelle grâce à des ingrédients soigneusement sélectionnés :

- Sphères d’acide hyaluronique pour des lèvres lissées et préservées de la déshydratation.
- Beurre de mangue aux propriétés nourrissantes pour des lèvres douces comme du velours.
- Micro-nacres ton sur ton qui réfléchissent la lumière pour un fini mat métallique unique.

💄 J'adore l'idée de pouvoir choisir l'écrin, de pouvoir le faire graver, le personnaliser fait de ce rouge à lèvres un accessoire unique, je le trouve vraiment superbe et exceptionnel ! La forme de cet écrin et la forme bisauté du rouge à lèvres permet une application précise. Sa texture est très agréable, il glisse sur les lèvres. Ce rouge 966 Red Fire Star est très pigmenté, il apporte une haute couvrance, un fini métallisé très confortable. C'est une couleur très sensuelle qui sublime une femme pour une journée entière, sa tenue est parfaite. Je suis sous le charme. 

💄Parfois je porte des teintes claires, parfois des teintes plus soutenues toute dépend de ma tenue, de mon humeur, oui mon état d’esprit rentre en compte. Quand je me sent bien je porte facilement du rouge. 

C'est bientôt la Saint Valentin n'ayez pas peur de sublimer vos  lèvres aux couleurs de l'amour.

Un immense merci aviquali_officiel et guerlain pour la confiance accordée.

JARDIN DE PARFUMS TRILOGY

[#AD] Do you like giveaways? 🗨️

▶️ Today I'll give an impression of these 3 releases from Jardin de Parfums. I'll be giving away a bottle of 23 Voyage later this week, so stay tuned for that if you're interested!

1️⃣ 23 VOYAGE is my favorite and the one I'd recommend blindly the most of these, so it was a good pick for the giveaway. I'd describe it as an aromatic amber/vanilla with woody touches. A bright citrussy top, instantly followed by vanilla. There's a hint of sharpness and a slightly green aromatic feeling. Some acidity lasts, but it rather quickly becomes a straight-up sweet and easy to wear vanilla drydown with a dry paper-esque woody tinge. It's cozy, but it lasts well.

2️⃣ ORACLE starts off as the most interesting and unique one, as its essentially a coconut scent. It's been compared to Black Orchid, but Oracle is brighter and lighter, easier to wear. This one opens slightly fruity, fig-like and definitely has that signature Black Orchid tinge at first, but transitions into more of a lactonic coconut, sun-tan territory. I really like the opening, but the fruity sweetness gets a bit cloying in the drydown for me.

3️⃣ PAPAVERO NERO is a rose-oud that won't surprise most of you. It smells good (probably better than the other two quality-wise to me), but it's been done before. It's a cleaner, saffrony-leather hidden underneath a rose that becomes a tad soapy, with a conventional, safe oud, making it accessible. Nero is being compared to Roja's Amber Aoud, but don't expect that kind of quality here.

⏺️ In general, I was happy with the scents, but quality-wise they leave something to be desired. As do the caps, the atomizers. The bottles look good (and the unboxing is beautiful actually), but it's not quite there in the details.

Price-wise they're solid and the scent profiles of 23 Voyage and Oracle are interesting, but the fragrances have a generic 'straight from an affordable factory' feeling to them in my opinion. As a self-certified niche snob, they didn't fully appeal to me. I know that a lot of people will feel differently though, so you'll have to try for yourself... or win this week's giveaway of course.

#MAKEUP: Hoje vamos falar dos de um dos Lançamentos mais aguardados dos últimos tempos. A Paleta de Sombras da Coleção Minnie Mouse All Eyes On Minnie da parceria da brunatavares com nada menos que a Walt Disney World #waltdisneyworld 

Pra quem conhece já as sombras da linhabrunatavares, pode esperar um booooom de qualidade nessa nova paleta! Sério! A Bruna deu um Upgrade nas suas novas fórmulas de sombras! Tô cho-ca-da! 

A paleta All Eyes On Minnie é uma paleta de sombras com embalagem exclusiva da fofíssima Minnie Mouse, em preto e metalizado rose gold, também acompanha um espelho de ótima qualidade! A paleta é pesadinha e super bem acabada.

A paleta possui 9 cores em vários acabamentos como folheado brilhante, cintilante perolado, iridescente e matte aveludado. 

Ao toque eu fiquei muito impressionada pois senti que são suuuuuper aveludadas, permitem construção de camadas e esfumam muito bem. Eu adorei que os pans são com ótimo acabamento na paleta. São mais altinhos e muito fáceis de aplicar. 

Uma curiosidade seria que as fórmulas das sombras possuem fórmula com Nylon e Vitamina E. 

E ahhh para usar algumas texturas de algumas sombras, a Bruna sugere que vocês usem o BtGlue! Mas senti que super da uma grudadinha nos olhos. 

Lembrando uma coisa super importante: É edição limitada! Então corre pra garantir a sua! 

Apesar do preço ser um pouco maior que as outras paletas da linha. Eu senti que foi super justo. Pois temos que lembrar que é uma parceria e é um produto de edição mais luxuosa e de maior qualidade! 

(Preço: R$ 145,00).

𝐌𝐚𝐬𝐜𝐚𝐫𝐚 « 𝐒𝐢𝐳𝐞 𝐔𝐩 » 𝐝𝐞 𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐳 sephoracollection ✨

Hello les girls, j’espère que vous allez bien et que votre journée s’est bien passé ? 💬

Aujourd’hui, je vais vous parler du mascara « Size Up » de chez sephoracollection !

Commençons par le packaging, il est d’une couleur grise métallisée, avec l’inscription Size Up qui apporte une touche de couleur et pas des moindres avec le jaune fluo. Je ne le trouve pas particulièrement joli mais ça passe. 
Il a une contenance de 14ml ce qui est généreux, comparé à la plupart des mascaras d’autres marques qui font généralement 8 ou 10ml. 

Sa formule est vegan, ce qui est un très bon point pour moi. Sa brosse en forme de sablier a une taille parfaite, ni trop épaisse ni trop fine. Quand elle sort du tube, elle n’est pas saturée de matière. J’ai des cils assez longs, volumineux et courbés. Avec ce mascara, ils sont beaucoup plus allongé et donne l’impression que j’ai plus de cils, je trouve. Le mascara a une couleur très noire sur les cils et c’est ce que j’aime également. Sur mes cils, je mets maximum deux couches pour avoir le rendu souhaité sinon je trouve sur tous les autres mascaras que ça donne un effet pattes d’araignée ce que je n’aime pas du tout. La tenue de ce mascara est très bonne, je n’ai rien à dire concernant ce sujet. Je vous le recommande les yeux fermés !

Niveau qualité prix, il est intéressant puisque ce format de 14ml ne coûte que 12,99€. Si vous voulez le tester, il existe aussi en format voyage de 5ml à 5,99€ chez sephora !

Yes or no?✨
By abramovskaya

Your own personal velvet commodity 

I don’t always do fragrance Friday, but when I do it’s one that you don’t want to miss. 

commodity Velvet- is from from the personal collection. Intentionally crafted to have a close projection; only meant for you and the few you allow close. (the perfect Valentine’s Day gift perhaps?)

There are plenty of classic romantic scents for Valentine’s Day, the delicate florals, inviting gourmands and beyond. But commodity offers something different.

In the first few seconds Velvet- truly captures the essence of velvet, throughout the day it takes me down a road of toasted almond and even fluffy roses drifting down a vanilla river. It’s perfect if you like something mysterious to warm you up on the cold days (and who doesn’t?)

Vanilla, Rose and Amber are made more sheer with Skin Musk, again intentionally crafted that way for a closer projection. But the rose in this fragrance is what I find most unique, sort of done in a powdery way and so complex that it’s not always detectable at every pass. With a smoky dry down that reveals it to be an unexpectedly soothing, warm, and comforting fragrance for these cooler seasons. And it’s definitely giving me all of the romantic yet modern vibes. 

What’s your favorite romantic perfume?

مصمم خصيصًا للبشرة المختلطة إلى الدهنية، يحتوي هذا القناع المصحح لعيوب البشرة  على طين طبيعي ومواد نباتية معروفة بخصائصها المنقية:

ورقة البوكو، توفر تأثيرًا قويًا مضادًا للبكتيريا
مستخلصات الجوجوبا تنظم إنتاج الدهون و تقلص حجم مسام البشرة.
بفضل تأثيره الماص للدهون والمقشر، يساعد قناع الطين المصحح للعيوب على تنظيف المسام بعمق دون تهيج الغدد الدهنية. وبالتالي، يساعد على تطهير البشرة من الشوائب ومكافحة الرؤوس السوداء والرؤوس البيضاء.

Spécialement formulé pour les peaux mixtes à grasses, ce masque anti-imperfections contient de l'argile naturelle et des actifs de plantes reconnus pour leurs propriétés purifiantes :
- la feuille de buchu, originaire d'Afrique du Sud, offre une puissante action antibacterienne
- les extraits de jojoba régulent la production de sébum et affinent le grain de peau.

Grâce à son action absorbante et exfoliante, le Masque à l'Argile Anti-Imperfections permet de nettoyer les pores en profondeur sans irriter les glandes sébacées. Il contribue ainsi à débarrasser la peau des impuretés et à lutter contre les points noirs et les comédons.

Proposé à prix mini, c'est le masque idéal pour faire peau nette et arborer un joli teint frais et mat !

✨Produtos pra usar uma vez e nunca mais largar✨

Oi, gente! 🤩

Nada melhor que gastar 💰 com produtos que valem a pena, né? E esses são alguns que vão te conquistar desde o 1° uso 🥹❤️.

👉🏻 Loção facial hidratante Cerave (R$60,00): um dos hidratantes mais sequinhos que já testei q deixa a pele tão macia como uma seda, mas sem acrescentar textura e escorrer óleo durante o dia. Amo/sou usar antes da make e no meu dia a dia, seja na rotina ☀️ ou na 🌑. Tem ácido hialurônico, niacinamida que é um dos meus ativos favoritos e 3 ceramidas essenciais na fórmula.

👉🏻 Tinted balm Ruby Rose (R$10,00): sabemos que dona RR arrasa e esse balm é mais um hit da marca que vale a pena gastar teu dindin. Um balm hidratante que resgata os teus beicinhos do ressecamento enquanto deixa uma corzinha linda and natural.

👉🏻 Ma chérie O Boticário (R$103,90 na promo): preciso falar algo?? O ícone da infância de várias pessoas voltou e espero que seja pra ficar. Um cheirinho que remete a infância e traz uma sensação única de conforto que só usando pra saber. Desde 1997 um floral musk que conquista narizes e pessoas.

👉🏻 Desodorante antitranspirante Natura (R$26,90): pra quem não gosta de outros tipos de desodorante (roll on, aquele que sai fazendo xiiii q não lembro o nome, em pedra e etc), esse em creme é uma opção 10/10 pq é daqueles que tu pode percorrer o deserto 🏜 que não sei o resto, mas teu subaquinho permanecerá intacto, cheiroso e sem transpiração.

👉🏻 Máscara big by definition Sephora (comprei um kit com gloss por R$90,00): cara? Sim, mas eu to chocada em Cristo o que ela fez pelos meus cílios 😱😱 os bichos tocam na sobrancelha quando uso e não sai por nada! Posso suar e chorar que a máscara não desgruda de mim.

👉🏻 Cleansing oil BM Skin (R$129,90): mais um cleansing oil pra colocar na listinha quando entrar em promo pq realmente vale a pena. Tira TUDO, de make a pecados e grudes mais resistentes, inclusive as máscaras a prova d’água. Não ardeu nos zoi e tirou tudo com uma facilidade de cair queixos. AMEI!

📍Onde encontrar? Todos vendem em lojas on-line e em algumas lojas físicas.

𝐋𝐞𝐬 𝐩𝐚𝐥𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐬 « 𝐂𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐦𝐞𝐥 𝐌𝐞́𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐞 » 𝐞𝐭 « 𝐂𝐨𝐜𝐨𝐚 𝐁𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐝 » 𝐝𝐞 𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐳 zoevacosmetics ✨

Hello les girls, j’espère que vous allez bien? Comment se passe votre dimanche? 💬

Aujourd’hui, je vais vous parler des palettes « Caramel Mélange » et « Cocoa Blend » de chez zoevacosmetics qu’on peut retrouver chez sephorafrance ! ☺️

Le packaging est en carton, les abords de la palette sont aimantées et il n’y a pas de miroir ni de pinceau. Le packaging des palettes me fait penser à une tablette de chocolat ! 😋
Dans ces palettes, nous trouvons des fards mattes et irisés. Caramel Mélange est une palette ayant des fards chaud tandis que la Cocoa Blend est une palette avec des fards plus neutres, dans les tons beige, brun et rose cendré. 

Les fards s’appliquent bien, s’estompent très bien et sont très pigmentés que ce soit au niveau des fards mattes ou irisés. Malheureusement, il y a quelques chutes mais rien de méchant.

Je suis toujours aussi ravie des palettes Zoeva, bien que je trouve que certains swatches de certains fards ne ressemblent pas vraiment au fard en lui-même mais c’est qu’un détail. Je suis ravie de la pigmentation et du choix des couleurs. Pour moi, les palettes Zoeva sont excellentes pour celles qui débutent en maquillage mais également pour les plus expérimentés. D’autant plus, qu’elle coûte seulement 28€ ce qui est abordable pour le prix d’une palette à mon goût. 

Et vous, qu’en pensez-vous de ces palettes? Et de la marque zoevacosmetics ? 💬

.

Spring and summer skin incoming 🌸 blush is one of my favourite products during the warmer months to add a hint of colour and an element of brightness back into the complexion after foundation and concealer. These are my two favourite powder blush formulas…

🌸 MONOCHROME MOMENT VELVET BLUSH by PatrickTaBeauty

The blush that got me into blush. With a super smooth and highly pressed formula, this buttery powder lightly layers colour onto the skin without making it look matte and flat. With buildable pigmentation, I love how I can apply a little or a lot with ease, and it never ever looks patchy. My favourite shade is She’s Seductive, a browny rose, which suits everybody I know. 

🌸 AMBIENT LIGHTING BLUSH by HourglassCosmetics 

Another super smooth formula, but this time handmade into an intricate swirl of colour. The marble-effect look is created by combining the blush pigment with a complimentary tone of the brand’s iconic Ambient Lighting Powder, creating a formula that is smooth, radiant and blurring on the skin. My favourite shade is Diffused Heat, a gorgeous coral. 

To read more about all the products I believe you must have in your makeup collection, go to victoriavale.com to see more.

One of the palettes I received as a birthday gift last year was the natashadenona My Dream Palette. 

The palette at least to me has a bit of everything to meet a wide variety of tastes. It brings together lots of different shade families rather than sticking to one singular theme. 

It’s got a great mix of neutrals, a bit of plums, a hue of golds and a black that makes for a fantastic eyeliner shade. 

The formula of these shadows is really good. Buttery mattes that blend seamlessly and shimmer shades which hardly had any fall out.

🌟 Base Pro Filt'r soft mate de fentybeauty es un dolor más que una decepción. La base me encanta como queda peeeero es usarla y llenarme de textura y granos allá donde toca.

🌟 Eye Canvas de technic_cosmetics_es . En este caso estoy segura de que el fallo no es tanto de la marca como del vendedor. El producto esta TAN seco que es imposible que se venda así y cause tanto furor y viniendo de pprimor no es algo que pueda comprobar porque no tengo la tienda aquí.

🌟 Los lápices de danessamyricks_europe . Doy gracias a la beautifybox_es por existir y haberlos  podido probar por una fracción de su precio porque sino desde aquí me íbais a escuchar chillar . Por eso cajitas como esta son una maravilla porque nos ayudan a probar cosas y a no arruinarnos en el intento.

🌟 El labial de zara que me llegó no una sino dos veces lleno de moho... ¿no creo que os tenga que decir más, no? Sin embargo, he decidido darle otra oportunidad a Zara, ya os contaré más adelante.

🌟 El Graphic Liner de makeupforever ... que no está la cosa como para que la alta gama ande fallando en básicos. Que delineadores de 5 euros se lo comen con patatas...

Witajcie Kochani.

Tym razem w ofercie marki pixibeauty pojawiała się seria KOSMETYKÓW OCZYSZCZAJĄCYCH - CLARITY COLLECTION.

Sprawdzą się one dla każdego rodzaju skóry, a szczególnie do cery atopowej, czy też problematycznej.

Mają one za zadanie rozwiązać problemy skórne, zmniejszyć rozszerzone pory, zwiększyć nawilżenie, a także przywrócić skórze równowagę.

Zalicza się do nich:
💙 ŻEL DO MYCIA TWARZY (Clarity Cleanser)

To produkt, który świetnie oczyszcza skórę i złuszcza. Przy tym ją nawilża, koi, a także odświeża. Ponadto odblokowuje pory oraz przeciwdziała powstawaniu niedoskonałości.

💙 TONIK OCZYSZCZAJĄCY DO TWARZY (Clarity Tonic)

Bardzo dobrze złuszcza, oczyszcza skórę odblokowując też pory. A dodatkowo nawilża oraz koi.

💙 WODNE SERUM OCZYSZCZAJĄCE (Clarity Concentrate)

Spodobało mi się w nim to, iż fajnie nawilża skórę, reguluje wydzielanie sebum, ściąga rozszerzone pory, złuszcza oraz ujednolica koloryt cery. Sprawia, że skóra jest gładka w dotyku.

💙 DELIKATNY BALSAM NAWILŻAJĄCY (Clarity Lotion)

Posiada lekką, beztłuszczową konsystencję. Zapewnia skórze większe nawilżenie i matowe wykończenie. Zmniejsza wydzielanie sebum oraz widoczność porów.

💙 ŻEL PUNKTOWY (Zero Zit)

Ma on lekką konsystencję. Fajne jest w nim to, że szybko się wchłania. Pomaga zminimalizować zaczerwienienia, obrzęki i zapobiega wypryskom.

I powiem Wam, że te kosmetyki idealnie wpasowują się w moje potrzeby. Jeśli i Ty marzysz o skórze bez skazy to ta seria jest idealna dla Ciebie.

Na który z kosmetyków się skusisz?

💞February 2022 purchases💞

Ok, that's a lot of make up to buy in a month!
Let's see if I still love them 12 months later

💞vievemuse Shimmer Eye Wand (Old Gold) and Modern Matte Lipstick (Lara). I didn't use them much in 12 months (less than 10X). The wand is cute but I always forget about it. I like the shade of the pstick but I am not a fan of the formula (too drying for my liking)

💞narsissist Climax palette. The palette that started my love for greens. I went back and forth for months on this palette, but luckly I got her before it was too late

💞lysbeautyofficial Higher Standard Satin Matte Cream Blush (Confident and Kindness) and Aim High Pressed Powder Highlighter (Genuine). While I adored the blushes (the formula is included in my top of 2022), I quite disliked the highlighter. 

💞rarebeauty Soft Pinch Liquid Blush (Love) and Positive Light Liquid Luminizer (Mesmerize). I used the highlighter a lot, while the blush didn't get enough love. I really like the formula, but the shade is actually pretty similar to Confident and I prefer Lys blushes (they are easier to use IMO)

💞sephoracollection Colorful Eyeshadows (First Light and Ultraviolet). While I used First Light a lot, Ultraviolet was forgotten. It is beautiful but It's not a shade a tend to use on everyday base (and that's reminds me that I don't need the new CT pop shot if I didn't use this enough)

I definetely need to be more mindful with my purchases. The things I still love and use are the ones that were in my wishlist for quite sometimes, while all the impulse purchases tend to be forgotten.

Hello les girls, j’espère que vous allez bien et que votre journée s’est bien passée ? 💬

Aujourd’hui, je vais vous parler du fond de teint Born This Whay Matte de chez toofaced en teinte Porcelaine. Je cherchais un fond de teint couvrant mais avec un fini naturel sachant que je me maquille très peu le teint, seulement pour les grandes occasions ou que j’ai tout simplement envie donc la conseillère de Sephora m’a présentée et testée celui-ci. 

La version classique du fond de teint Born this way existe depuis 2015. La version matte est sortie en France en septembre 2020. Je ne souhaitais pas prendre la version classique, car il ne me correspond pas à mon type de peau et je n’aime pas le rendu qu’il me donne.

Il regroupe tout ce que j’apprécie et je recherchais. Un fond de teint avec un rendu naturel, une couvrance modulable, une tenue qui dure dans la journée, pas de transfert et une résistance au port prolongé du masque ! J’aime bien l’appliquer à la beauty blinder et à fin de la journée, je n’ai pas besoin de poudrer ma zone T (J’ai une peau mixte à grasse). 

Il est au prix de 41€ chez sephora en magasin ou sur leur site internet. Le fond de teint est de 30ml 😊

Everything has to run smoothly on a set because "time is money," so you get an inside look at what actually works in the hair and beauty world - they don't have time to use crappy products. The day after the cat died (😭🐈), we all had super puffy eyes from crying. Azi needed to NOT look completely different from every other episode out of nowhere... so the makeup team cured the puffy eyes with these eye masks. 

Azi said they made him feel much better, so a few days later he asked to do the "luxurious" masks again just because they made his eyes feel so nice. I couldn't remember what they were but he said he thought they were something to do with Iceland. I gave him a pair from my own stash but apparently the ones I have on hand are not the quality he desires now that he's had the best 😅. A quick Google and sephoracanada search and we found what he was looking for. I was... surprised what the nice ones cost (heh) but they actually totally 100% worked so at least I know why...

So that is how we came to order skyniceland eye masks for our 9-year-old 😂😬

I strongly encourage beauty companies to sponsor HMU teams, because now you have a customer for life, and 9 is a pretty young age to start 🤣.

He is at school now so I think I will steal a pair for myself.

💄 Cuando utilizo coloretes en crema a veces me gusta utilizar un colorete en polvo encima para que la duración de ambos producto sea muchísimo más larga. Los utilizo solo? Si, tanto los cremosos como los coloretes en polvo y TODOS, absolutamente todos los coloretes que ves aquí me encantan tanto solos como acompañados. 

💄 Me ha costado mucho hacer la selección, porque yo mezclo mucho, pero sobre todo también me ha costado porque he intentado poner coloretes que actualmente podéis conseguir. En mi día a día utilizo muchísimos más coloretes, pero desafortunadamente ya no están a la venta. 

💄Todas las mezclas que verás en este post han sido probadas por mi. Con este post EN NINGÚN MOMENTO busco encontrar un clon, para nada. Solo os muestro las mezclas que yo hago y nada más. Algunas se parecen, otras nada, como por ejemplo el colorete de Mac y de Benefit, pero que en el rostro quedan increíblemente bonitos. En definitiva buscar productos que entre ellos casen bien y me hagan sentir que llevo una mejilla bonita y de muy larga duración. Por supuesto que hay miles de mezclas, infinidad de ellas, no te quedes solo con lo que ves aquí. 

💄 Y nada más! Creo que no se me olvida nada, espero que os guste, porque de verdad... me ha costado la vida hacerlo! Porque además, como ya os he dicho he probado cada una de ellas, para saber si me gustaban o no. 

💄Espero que os guste, si es así que le des ❤️ porque a mi me ayuda mucho, además de entender que mi contenido te gusta. Te leo en comentarios, y si lo compartes te lo agradezco mil ❤️❤️❤️

Z okazji ostatnich urodzin udało mi się spełnić jedno z perfumowych marzeń, a konkretniej - po dwóch latach odhaczyć na liście zakupów (z 2020 roku) ostatni punkt 😁 W moje łapki wreszcie wpadł uroczy flakonik YSL Libre ✌️

Gdybym miała opisać Libre jednym zdaniem, powiedziałabym że są eleganckie, ostre i wyrafinowane. Gdybym mogła użyć większej ilości słów, dodałabym, że są niezwykłym połączeniem ziół, owoców i kwiatów. A i to nie zobrazowałoby zapachu. Nie umiem bezbłędnie rozpoznać nut użytych w perfumach - a i posiłkując się listą tychże, nie każdą odnajdę. Pominę też fakt, że każdy odbiera zapach ciut inaczej i na każdej skórze perfumy inaczej się układają. 
Dla mnie Libre to przede wszystkim soczysta i ostra mandarynka 🍊 mistrzowsko połączona z ziołową lawendą, świeżą i rześką 🍃 Całość doprawiona jest białym kwieciem, słodką wanilią i otulającym ciepłym drewnem.  Ale to duet mandarynki i lawendy gra pierwsze skrzypce i przez długie godziny dominuje 💜

Libre to wolność 💚 Czy można ją poczuć w zapachu tych perfum ?? 
Abstrahując od marketingowych wytyczonych, w których dodatek "męskiej lawendy" do stricte kobiecych perfum uwalnia je spod jarzma konwenansów - dla mnie Libre to zapach przestrzeni i świeżego powietrza 🍃 To wolność rozumiana w sensie dosłownym - dzikość, natura, brak ograniczeń i barier 🌿 Połączenie ziół, owoców i kwiatów w kompozycję popularną i "dla wszystkich" daje prywatne poczucie osobistej wolności nawet w wielkim mieście 💚
Perfumy zaskakują trwałością, utrzymują się na skórze bardzo długo 🍃

Spełniacie swoje marzenia - te kosmetyczne i nie tylko ??😉💚

Cheirosa ‘62 is viral but have you guys smelt Cheirosa ‘40?? 😩

#soldejaneirogiftedme | Cheirosa ‘40 is apart of the soldejaneiro Bom Dia Bright collection and dare I say . . . I might prefer it over my beloved Cheirosa ‘62 scent ?!

The Brazilian Crush Cheirosa 40 Bom Dia Bright™ Perfume Mist smells like a summery, elevated vanilla with layers of plum + jasmine. It also smells faintly clean to me . . . you know that feeling when you get out of the shower and you can smell your body wash on you? It gives me that feeling when I spray it if that makes sense, but at the same time, it doesn’t have any typical “clean” notes like citrus or lavender. It’s hard to explain but it just makes me feel so clean, put together, and like I have a tan! 😌

I’ve talked about Sol De Janeiro perfume mists 10000 times before, but they’re SO good and I’m slowly growing my collection! If Cheirosa ‘62 is too sugary for you, you’d love this one! I honestly think I love both scents depending on how I want to feel; both of them have a time and place for me (me saying this to avoid picking a fav) 🫡

Which one do YOU like though? 👀 *you can say both hehe*

Lip Stain линията продукти на sephoracollection е нещото, което винаги трябва да ви вълнува, пазарувате ли от SEPHORA! Сами виждате колко притежавам аз…и продължавам да си купувам нови цветове, но и любими такива! 

💄Sephora Collection Cream Lip Stain Liquid Lipstick не е кое да е течно матово червило! То е ТЕЧНОТО матово червило. Простичката опаковка вероятно ще ви заблуди каква невероятна формула се крие в нея. Обогатено е с масло от авокадо и затова се плъзга по устните като маслен фин крем, но се превръща малко след това в копринено гладък матов отпечатък на нещо, което не мърда цял ден! Не се разтича, не се размазва, не хуква по линийките и поричките около контура на устните! Много фин филм, но силна пигментация! Не се усеща прекалено сухо на устните! Търпи промяна на цвета след засъхване, което е повече от нормално! 

📈Sephora Collection Lip Stain Liner е автоматичен, кремообразен молив за устни, които засъхне ли, не мърда никъде! Мек е и с него се работи бързо и прецизно! Може да го ползвате самостоятелно, като запълните устните; може да го ползвате като контур заедно с любимо червило или гланц; може да го ползвате като гъвкава дълготрайна основа под червило…може дори да смесите няколко цвята от молива на устните си… Правете, каквото искате с този молив - той ще бъде там, за вас! 

🌟 Тези продукти не излизат от гримьорския ми куфар и са ми верни помощници в създаването на устойчива грим визия! 

😇 Може ли да познаете, от показаните цветове кои са мои любимци? 

*На снимките вече няма такива продукти, които са ми пратени от sephora.bulgaria! Всички са подновени, като съм си ги купила сама. 
*Постът не е спонсориран!

My newest shade of charlottetilbury Eyes to Mesmerize Cream Eyeshadow in Pillow Talk! 

This is a gorgeous, dusty pink shade of a formula I have been loving. I also have the Chocolate Bronze shade which I am completely obsessed with. When I first bought one of these, I was hesitant because I did hear mixed reviews about it. But I have to say, I loveee this eyeshadow. 

This creates such a pretty, glowy eye look. Sometimes I add a sparkly topper to it, but it’s also beautiful on its own. The pigment lasts all day (I wear it to work), and I do get some mild creasing after several hours, but I haven’t experimented much with setting my eyelids (other than powder).

Overall I really enjoy these cream eyeshadows and would keep adding to my collection! Have you tried any of these?

February's Empties and Speed Reviews!! LETS GO!!!

sioris_global My First Essencer- I loved it!! Very hydrating and soothing. The only issue was something was wrong with my lid, and it got nasty and wouldn't seal up. 

caudalieus Grape Water Mist - LOVE spray water!! It's a sensitive skin person's savior!! Use to hydrate and moisten between steps. 

drunkelephant Wonderwild Miracle Butter - Not a fan. Mine was gritty and had a whole bunch of oil that would come out each time I used it. 

soldejaneiro Brazilian Crush 71 - HOLY GRAIL scent. I mix it with all kinds of fragrances to add a sweet vanilla smell. 

clarity_rx  Hyaluronic Acid - It was a good HA.  No foaming or sticky feeling. It was thick and hard to get out of the bottle at the end. 

iunik_official Black Snail Restore Cream - I loved the snail texture. It was thick and occlusive without being suffocating. Would buy again!!

farmacybeauty Filling Good - This didn't work out. It foamed up almost every time I used it and has a pretty strong scent that smelt a little off. 

beekman1802 MilkShake Toner - 10 out of 10 I will always have this. It tones, hydrates, and plumps all in one step. I use it almost every day!

Happy Sunday! 🤍

Here’s a sneak peek into all my opened serums right now. 😅 I’ll be honest and say I didn’t realise I had this many opened, especially as I’ve offloaded quite a bit to my cousin and sisters this summer!

My skincare goal for 2023 is to use up more of the products I have and reduce on the spending. If I can’t use it up, then pass it on to someone who’ll benefit more from it. So grateful my cousin’s skin isn’t sensitive because she literally uses all the products I give to her with no issues.

I’m almost finished with Beauty of Joseon ginseng and snail serum, Cosrx the niacinamide 15 serum and Axis-Y dark spot correcting glow serum. So once they’re done, I’ll be able to focus more on the other opened ones.

So far, the only skincare purchases I’ve made this year are sunscreens that are on sale at half price. Sunscreens don’t count, as I use them daily for protection and not really anything else. I use them up quicker too.

Can you relate with the opened serums or am I just not okay? 😅

[SOBRE PARADAS] 🪬🚫‼️🛑
Com certeza eu posso me acostumar e dificilmente venha a cansar de ter tempo para mim. 
Nos meus momentos de mim pra mim, tenho percebido tanta vida que não conseguia absorver antes. 
Quando estou na #sogipa eu vivo pra mim, e isso não é egoísmo. É cuidar de mim, entre VITAMINA D, mergulho, exercícios e leituras sou interrompida pelo sinal do colégio que fica perto e penso...como é possível ser condicionada a um sinal de entrar e sair, de correr de um lugar para outro.
🚨🚫Um sinal. Um toque de parar. De iniciar. A gente fala tanto em mudanças na educação e algumas coisas simples ...simplesmente não mudam. 
Há alunos e alunas que são sensíveis à sirenes e sons altos. 
Já trabalhei em escolas que o som era a música da MISSÃO IMPOSSÍVEL - não fiquei um semestre, entendi rapidamente e com muita dor psicológica o porquê desse sinal (esse capítulo estará no livro - diário que vou escrever sobre ser PROFESSORA) 
Sei que a vida não nos permite essas pausas , às vezes não nos damos o direito, eu entendo tudo isso. 

É uma decisão difícil - PARAR - não ter planejamento do planejamento do planejamento ...♾️♾️., nem e-mails em todos os horários (ainda me sinto presa a esse hábito de ter medo das mensagens). 
❤️❤️❤️❤️SER PROFESSORA em sala de aula é uma dádiva, um dom, uma terapia -AMO. ❤️💎Viveria só disso, de juventude, de intensidade, de trocas, de ensinar.
"SALVEM A (à)PROFESSORINHA"

O resto todo, aos poucos estou me desligando. 

Então sim, nesse momento sou EU pra mim. 🪞🥰♀️

selflessbyhyram launched in June 2021 with sephora as its exclusive retail partner. The global retailer unceremoniously dumped it after only 18 months on the shelves. When this news broke, we assumed Selfless was on its way to the place where influencer and celebrity brands go to die.

But Gen-Z skin-fluencer hyram Yarbro refused to be broken and tossed aside by Sephora's notoriously fickle (and often misguided) marketers and merchandisers.

Selfless by Hyram, in a bold post-Sephora pivot, is moving to target - and lowering its product prices.

Yarbro, who has 6.5 million followers on TikTok, 4.55 million on YouTube, and 976,000 on Instagram, has always recommended "drugstore" skincare on his social platforms because that's where the majority of his followers shop. 

The new online and in-store partnership with Target (beginning February 5th) retails the formerly $16-$30 products for only $13-$24. Much more in line with Mass-market skincare brands like larocheposay, neutrogena, olay, and L'Oreal Revitalift. It also gives the brand additional exposure in the over 300 ultabeauty "Target" shop-in-shops, alongside naturiumskin, founded by fellow skin-fluencer susanyara.

Regarding the company's state, Yarbo said in an interview, "We're still charging full speed ahead...Target represents what I've always wanted the brand to be, which is more accessible." 

What do you think about this move? 
Will it save Selfless by Hyram?

The new online and in-store partnership with Target (beginning February 5th) retails the formerly $16-$30 products for only $13-$24. Much more in line with Mass-market skincare brands like larocheposay, neutrogena, olay, and L'Oreal Revitalift. It also gives the brand additional exposure in the over 300 ultabeauty "Target" shop-in-shops, alongside naturiumskin, founded by fellow skin-fluencer susanyara.

Regarding the company's state, Yarbo said in an interview, "We're still charging full speed ahead...Target represents what I've always wanted the brand to be, which is more accessible."

Hello les girls, j’espère que vous allez bien? 💬

Aujourd’hui, je vais vous présenter le best-seller de la marque qui est l’anti-cerne « Shape Tape » de chez tartecosmetics qui est disponible chez sephora ! 

Commençons par le packaging, je le trouve très sympa, en particulier grâce au joli bouchon. L’applicateur mousse intégré est un plus, il permet de gagner du temps lors de l’application. Si je devais donner un petit défaut, ce serait l’embout mousse qui est bien trop gros pour un anti-cernes d’autant plus qu’il met beaucoup trop de matière à mon goût. 

La formule est excellente, c’est une texture un peu crémeuse, mais assez coulante donc le juste milieu pour avoir un produit pas trop compact mais qui s’étale parfaitement sans couler. En plus, elle ne laisse aucune sensation grasse sur la peau. En se matifiant, elle sèche en se matifiant, mais sans laisser de sensation de tiraillement sur la peau. Il a une couvrance assez forte mais pas visible et une très bonne pigmentation. Il couvre très bien les imperfections et les cernes visibles. Vous pouvez vraiment l’ajuster en fonction du nombre d’applications. En plus des cernes, il peut parfaitement camoufler les petites imperfections, les rougeurs et les cicatrices d’acné. 

La formule a une légère odeur de parfum qui ne me dérange pas plus que ça, au contraire. Le rendu est très joli et plutôt naturel. Il s’agit d’un fini plutôt mat, il ne marque pas trop les zones de sècheresses ni les ridules sauf si on n’en met beaucoup trop. Niveau sensation, il est assez léger, on ne sent pas d’épaisseur sur la peau. La tenue est plutôt très bonne. Il est longue tenue en toute fin de journée, il commence à filer un peu dans les ridules, c’est très léger.

Il contient 10ml en étant au prix de 24€. Il est disponible chez tartecosmetics et chez sephorafrance !

Happy water shot Wednesday with a new one from peterthomasrothofficial ! 

A primer with added skincare ingredients? Sign me up. 

I have large pores, so I’m always on the hunt to blur and smooth them. And I love trying primers with even temporary effects. 
Instant FIRMx No-Filter Primer has been really impressive! The tint is invisible once applied so it’s not a must to layer makeup over top, if you like the simplistic blurring effect like I do, just apply and go. However it does keep makeup in place for ages! So if you have a hard time with makeup sliding around, give it a try for that too, it might work like a charm for that matte and airbrushed look. 
I thought this would be thick and silicone-y but it’s actually kind of thin. It wasn’t what I was expecting- but that wasn’t a bad thing - It’s genius really. 

They used a blend of skin-tightening silicates and seaweed extract coined as Firm-A-Tite™. In addition, 3% BarPull enhances the instant effect while hydrating skin and providing long-term anti-aging benefits. 

In a nutshell? Easy to use for everyday, keep in mind a little goes a long way, and suitable for all skin tones and types, even those with less advanced signs of aging. 

What do you think, will you check out the newest addition to the Instant FIRMx family?

Toda hora aparece um novo, né?

Bernard Arnault, o novo (homem, velho e branco) mais rico do mundo tem 73 anos de idade, é francês, CEO e dono de 48% da LVMH - um conglomerado de luxo, dona de 75 marcas como Dior, Givenchy, Sephora, Bulgari, TAG Hauer, Louis Vuitton, Chandon, etc…

Arnault só atingiu esse posto após a fortuna de Elon Musk (que chegou a US$ 340 bilhões) cair para US$ 158 bilhões após a aquisição da “rede do passarinho” - isso também o tornou a 1ª pessoa da Europa a atingir o 1º lugar na lista da Forbes dos mais ricos.

Embora a vasta fortuna do francês seja muito menor que a de Musk no auge, o empresário conseguiu construir um baita império enquanto tinha uma vida relativamente tranquila - mas, acho importante lembrar que, assim como Musk, Arnault já vinha de uma família muito rica.

Com uma vida discreta, Arnault é um ávido colecionador de arte - possuindo US $10,3 bilhões investidos nisso - e é pai de 5 filhos, com todos trabalhando no negócio da família como diretores ou vice-presidentes.

Hi Everyone! 🤗

I’ve been feeling extremely creative and original lately and as evidence I thought I would repost this look from a few months ago 🥸

I thought it would be fun to loosely base a look on a Bollywood movie- I grew up watching these movies with my siblings and cousins here in Canada and have a million memories associated with them. ❤️ This makeup look is based on Madhuri Dixit’s character from the movie “Devdas”(2002).

I wasn’t sure what colors to use because the lighting, filters etc in the movie made it hard to determine so I just guessed. 🤷🏽‍♀️

I tried recreating a similar pose, which was really difficult because Madhuri is an amazing dancer and was in a graceful dancing pose here. I, on the other hand look like I stepped on a hot tac when dancing 💃🏽😳 so I had to settle with looking like I’m doubled over with stomach pain. 

For this look I used my:
natashadenona “Lila” palette (Amara, Purpure) on lids (second picture)

#Paradise marcjacobsfragrances influenster 

I recieved this perfume for free from Influenster & Marc Jacobs in exchange for my honest opinion. 

Paradise by Marc Jacobs is a brand new limited edition, Eau De Toilette, release. It is categorized in the Warm & Spicy fragrance family with Key notes of Iris, Patchouli &  Sorbetto. I have looked & can not find a list of all the definite notes.  Fragrantica lists Iris as the top Note,  Patchouli as the heart & Whipped Cream as the base note. This fragrance is a floral & free spirited scent & is inspired by rare, natural beauty. 

This one is fun... youthful & beautiful. It is just a tad bit powdery on my skin and sweet. But not overly sweet.  It is perfectly balanced so it would be safe to wear as a teenager or in your 50s!  I love the scent of Irises. For an Eau De Toilette... It has excellent performance. I get a solid 6 hours out of it. It has good sillage too. This one is very layerable & I will most likely use it that way.  For me... It is a rather simple scent & mixing it to give it depth is what I plan on doing🌸 But I LOVE it & am ecstatic to add it to my collection. 

The bottle is adorable! I'm not sure why I expected the flower lid to be easily breakable but it isn't. The petals are bendy and if you were to drop it.. It would not break.  I adore a pretty perfume bottle! 

This is my first experience with Marc Jacobs perfume & I am in love! Can't wait to try more💗 Available sephora

#giftedbyarmani | I’m sure we’ve all collectively heard the hype around the armanibeauty Luminous Silk Foundation. I’m here to confirm: it is SO worth it!

I’ve been dealing with some closed comedones + red angry bumps (curtesy of my dermatitis ofc) and as a result, I try layering my foundation in attempts to get a smooth-looking base . . . but it just ends up looking cakey. Why am I saying this? Wellll, the Luminous Silk Foundation (shade 4.5) makes my skin texture look better with just one 1 pump! Did it make the irritation bumps disappear? Absolutely not because no makeup can do that. What it did do though was even out my skin tone and sink into my skin so seamlessly to where it overall looked smoother- it’s so hard to explain so iykyk 😩 I did some digging on the Armani Beauty website and they wrote that their micro–fil & trade technology creates that effect, so I probably have that to thank for what I was talking about!

Also, you guys all know I love to glow- tell me why I’ve never tried the Fluid Sheer Glow Enhancer (shade 2) until now?! It’s such a thin formula but it packs a punch in terms of glow, all while maintaining a natural glow-from-within quality. I don’t think I have to speak for it, just look at the glowy cheekbones 😩

It’s official, I’m now forever apart of the Armani Beauty fan club 🤍

Toners.. aka the skin ph balancer.
One of the purposes of a toner is to re-balance your skin’s ph levels.
Some toners can be too harsh and strip your skin of it’s natural oils! This can cause dryness, irritation and breakouts. 
Your skin’s natural ph is around 4.5, so pick a toner close to that ph level. 

One of my go to toners is the youthtothepeople Mandelic Acid + Superfood Unity Exfoliant. 
This toner doesn’t burn and calms my skin while removing any impurities my skin may have collected throughout the day. 

I use this after I cleanse twice at night and before I apply my targeted serum or cream. 
Happy Toning! 🧪

Need a unique Vanilla Fall Fragrance?

🥛Vanilla Milk by ellisbrooklyn is a warm and creamy vanilla. It’s designed to be worn best on skin with your body chemistry and body heat.

🤍Warm, Woody, Gourmand

🔑Key Notes
Bourbon Vanilla Bean Extract, Upcycled Cocoa Shell, Frangipani

⬆️Top:
Creamy Milk Accord, Frangipani, Peony Rose

➡️Mid:
Bourbon Vanilla Bean, Madagascar Vanilla Bean Extract, Upcycled Cocoa Shell Extract

⬇️Bottom:
Benzoin Resinoid, Amyris, Sandalwood, Musk

My Thoughts💭 :
This fragrance is a creamy, warm, and woody vanilla. I sometimes get a hint of an “incense” smell (I think from the woody notes). This makes for a really nice fall time scent because of how rich, creamy, and warm this vanilla is. I love how it’s sweet (but not too sweet) and it’s smooth. It different from most vanilla scents I have worn because of the woody dry down. Overall, definitely a must have for those looking for a more unique vanilla, but the creaminess may be too rich for some who like a more airy vanilla. I think it’s a lovely fragrance.

Your social media feeds are not real life. You scroll and scroll and feel like everyone else has a better body, better skin, more money, a better house - it’s easy to feel like everyone else is always better and doing more.

We have no idea what goes on behind the scenes of the aesthetic pictures and videos we see online. We don’t see people’s skin up close, we don’t always spot photo editing.

It’s important to remember that social media isn’t reality, and, even if so - someone else having what you want or doing well for themselves, does NOT mean that you lack. We are so, so hard on ourselves. We forget that everyone’s journey is different.

Have grace for yourself today. Remember that quite literally no one on this planet is perfect. Perfection isn’t realistic, but loving yourself through the ups and downs of life and holding space for yourself to be human? Possible and very much worth it.

How’s your self love journey today? I encourage you to check in with yourself. ❤️
